			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The Disk Drive cable itself is just three digital signals from the base station (written to via $4025), three signals from the base station (read via $4032), the battery voltage (read via $4033),  the serial transmit and receive streams, ground, +5V, and the twelfth pin is unused.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

